Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.01,0:00:34.06,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:04.15,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:19.88,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.85,0:14:29.89,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.45,0:27:20.49,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.74,0:29:19.78,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Epilogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.36,0:00:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry it had to come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.25,0:00:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.24,0:02:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?! That sounds like some cheesy movie title!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Legend of Narukami Yu: The Sacred Dragon Sword of Wrath"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he even fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a kung-fu movie, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.55,0:02:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! {\i1}I'm{\i0} the sponsor here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you're in such high spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks for having us over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your time with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.86,0:02:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{is this taste good enough?}can you try this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemme see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, it feels a bit too weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have that special kick to it.{so innovative: punch > kick}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about I add this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Should I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't! This is {\i1}your{\i0} going away party, after all!{lit you're the main hero today}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take it easy and chat with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.19,0:03:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And why are {\i1}you{\i0} taking it easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you've got a knack for this stuff, Tatsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.72,0:03:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How about putting this outside on the door?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.73,0:03:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{No, never and nope!}Oh, hell no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami, wanna taste it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have a taste of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you poison him at his going away party?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then{\i1} you{\i0} eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.00,0:03:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit, dude. A farewell party?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd actually leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine my days without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, you've got mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot to buy octopus for Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go back to get some!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about we go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you'll come back when you have time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think I'll come back during summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and the May holidays too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray! Then it's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.60,0:04:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna stay with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise you'll never forget me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.57,0:04:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami, wanna taste it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have a taste of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a knack for this stuff, Tatsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.51,0:05:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet that disgusting thing is what's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then{\i1} you{\i0} eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, you've got mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're surprised to get this letter out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm writing this because there's something I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that my game is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As you all insisted at the time, I'll abide by the rules of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's still this feeling I can't shake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about how it all started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,About that Midnight Channel...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{Now that I think about it more, before I'd even heard the rumors at the police,}Now I remember... Before I heard the rumors at the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{I think someone attacked me when I came to town.}Someone else told me about it when I first came to town...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.78,0:06:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was intrigued when I noticed that something similar was written on Namatame's report as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't remember who it was that told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Namatame and I both gained our power after coming to Inaba...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that had something to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if any of this will be useful or not, but I hope it can help somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The source of the Midnight Channel rumor
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and their powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You could use Personas from the very start and enter TVs too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you're a person who had power from the beginning, like Namatame and Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.91,0:06:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something beyond what we can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The Midnight Channel and the ability to enter TVs...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If they were really separate, they\N wouldn't fit together like this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So you think the person Adachi mentioned,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.74,0:07:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the one who told him about the Midnight Channel,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,also has something to do with the power to enter TVs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I strike gold again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... If they're somehow related...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, do you have any idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If we knew when you got your power to enter TVs,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we might be able to find the person who started the rumor of the Midnight Channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I got this power...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I remember having this dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the night I came to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Could that dream be the reason then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You had a dream without any discernible catalyst, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.83,0:07:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The day I arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember going straight to my uncle's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait! I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have a taste of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,remember the day I came to town?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.43,0:08:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We went somewhere before coming home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The gas station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When I got back from the bathroom,\N you were talking to the weird attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You looked sick after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.24,0:08:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.49,0:08:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're feeling sick, you should go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a weird question to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd make it all the way to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, I never expected this at all.\N You're really something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave the power to Adachi, Namatame, and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the handshake greeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A handful of strangers were more than sufficient to stimulate a small place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems the stimulus was stronger than I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.23,0:09:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It was enough to envelop this town with fog...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and later lift it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Izanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ameno-Sagiri, ruler of the fog, is merely an aspect of myself that I birthed long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.63,0:10:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You created the Midnight Channel and spread the rumors of its existence?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Close.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was I who created what you refer to as the Midnight Channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not the whole truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only been observing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.11,0:10:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{What is the world humans truly desire?}Has it not given you everything you've wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was always your individual wills that would determine what appeared on it.{You yourselves decided what you see there.}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans ache to expose their suppressed sides,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,while the prying eyes around them are curious to see them laid bare.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The want to show and the want to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I granted a "window" that catered to both.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's the Midnight Channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:11:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I merely gave you what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But I guess this comes with the foolish nature of being mortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{Your foolish desire to only see what you want to see drove the device.}The Midnight Channel only showed you what you wanted to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It showed you your desires in their purest form.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see how foolish you've been?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want the truth.{YOU CAN'T HANDLE THE TRUTH}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.54,0:11:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You see only what you want to see and believe only what you want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your desire is for a world enshrouded in fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,In eternal, never-lifting fog,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you will always see the world you want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{from kimitachi}That is true happiness for you humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How could a world covered in fog bring happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you honestly say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.49,0:11:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to see the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to remember the cruel reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Cruel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,640)}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the cruel reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to do better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{sensei}Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The will of all humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You disturb what they want to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.31,0:13:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,They desire to live in the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.29,0:13:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie! Help! Narukami!{narukami-kun?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stop! Please stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You only suffer because of your search for the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you should just live in a world covered by fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That is true happiness for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?! That sounds like some cheesy movie title!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Those're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a kung-fu movie, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be together forever, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm the only one who gets to be {\i1}together{\i0}-together with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There she goes again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have a taste of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you poison him—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{sensei}Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,How about putting this outside on the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Try putting these in too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.01,0:15:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that going a bit too far?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.89,0:15:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.{not nanako's pudding ;_;}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry it had to come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, you'll be okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that you'll come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you lose, Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I could break out of my slump thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He can read my moves?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{sensei}Thank you, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:18:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You taught me something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.00,0:18:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we're apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You helped me a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to be there for you, but it ended up the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But because of that, we became...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,a real family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid of a tomorrow without everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I was afraid I'd lose my friends and have to go on alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had my share of solitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.17,0:19:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to stay with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't care if it was just a illusion in the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to live a life without being connected to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.74,0:20:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care as long as I'm with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't need the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As long they're with me, I don't care if it's an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.88,0:20:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.14,0:20:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not alone anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you lose everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,your soul shall never be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Never forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.47,0:21:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a crystal of power which you have nurtured through your journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,An orb that repels fabrications of all sorts, dispels lies, and shines upon the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How have you returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.79,0:21:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's your true form?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.84,0:22:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It matters not.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The will of all mankind will pull you under again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.69,0:22:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Can the will of so few surpass the will of all mankind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.16,0:22:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Why don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible for humans to grasp the truth with their own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.75,0:22:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the one who gets to make that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.85,0:22:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friends are no longer with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.52,0:22:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you go on living alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.65,0:22:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.65,0:22:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,am not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of endless struggle, wouldn't it be easier to wrap oneself in lies and live in blissful ignorance?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.17,0:23:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to show you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,human potential!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.36,0:23:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think yourself a god?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.12,0:23:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.88,0:24:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If only they'd open their eyes and look ahead, they could see...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.55,0:24:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.38,0:24:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll dispel the fog that covers our path!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.93,0:24:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in the Myriad Truths{幾万の真言} ahead of us!{what was this in the game again? myriad truths or something?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.90,0:24:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Myriad Truths?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.20,0:24:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.82,0:24:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You have lifted the fog in this world, as well as the fog in your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.37,0:24:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And whether that will lead to happiness or not rests upon your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.38,0:24:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, leave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.92,0:24:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Children of man...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.84,0:24:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.27,0:24:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.56,0:25:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I still inside the TV world?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.52,0:25:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be what the TV world is supposed to look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.65,0:25:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{Wonderful! A wonderful turn of your life.}How marvelous! A turning point in your destiny, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.20,0:25:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This journey was a fruitful one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.95,0:25:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the fog of lies has lifted,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.20,0:25:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there is nothing to prevent you from moving forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.00,0:25:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You are free to walk your own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.17,0:25:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This will be the last time we summon you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.05,0:25:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.56,0:25:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.85,0:25:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.31,0:25:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.94,0:25:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.07,0:25:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to see this sight again for so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.07,0:25:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Everywhere in this world used to look like this a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.45,0:25:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, watch where you're rolling!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.91,0:25:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{senpai}You're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.83,0:25:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.20,0:25:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.33,0:26:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{senpai}Dude!{the fuck?}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.05,0:26:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Our contract has been fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.97,0:26:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My own duties end here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.14,0:26:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a truly remarkable guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.52,0:26:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go forth and see with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.78,0:26:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,976)}See the world you have won... \N{brainchild was here} And the bright, magnificent future...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.63,0:26:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,{added this line for the sake of timing, feel free to change/remove}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.67,0:26:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,see ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.05,0:26:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck over there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.14,0:26:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything happens on your end, we'll come running!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.26,0:27:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Until we meet again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.02,0:27:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be waiting for you!{gay}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.18,0:27:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye and take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.06,0:27:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be looking forward to seeing you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.56,0:27:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.86,0:27:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.19,0:27:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Buh-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.74,0:27:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.16,0:27:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You take care too!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.62,0:27:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.08,0:27:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay well until we meet again someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.75,0:27:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll always be my "Master"!{"You'll always be my bear-y best friend!"}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.75,0:27:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't forget about us over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.34,0:27:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.47,0:27:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.34,0:27:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best! You'd better not run away too!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.27,0:27:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always remember our time together!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.02,0:27:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Distance doesn't matter to us! Even if we're separated, we're still friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.19,0:27:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never, ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.16,0:27:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,forget you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.07,0:29:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.07,0:29:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sad he won't be around, but we'll be okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.79,0:29:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't matter how far apart we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.42,0:29:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{Our hearts are connected, that won't change!}{persona references in KC and KC references in persona. makes sense}The bonds we made will remain strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.67,0:29:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{You're connected with the people you trust.}Everyone's heart{kokoro} is connected to the people they know and trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.30,0:29:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's those bonds that let us all search for our purpose in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.14,0:29:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as it's a purpose you believe in,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.81,0:29:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,there'll always be someone who can help you fulfill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.27,0:29:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,For you, me, and everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.19,0:29:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no barriers. Our hearts are one.{THE WORLD INSIDE PEOPLE'S HEARTS OMG}
